<p>Implement the principles of <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/training/what-is-progressive-overload" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">progressive overload</a> discussed here in our article while using the information we’ve discussed regarding sets and reps. </p>



<p>To bring this all together, here’s an example of a hypertrophy-based push routine:</p>



