ilitary Press</td><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left">2–6 Sets</td><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">≤ 6 Reps @ >85% Of Your 1RM</td><td>2–5 Minutes</td><td></td></tr><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">Bodyweight Dip</td><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left">3–6 Sets</td><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">6–12 Reps @ 67%–85% Of Your 1RM</td><td>30–90 Seconds</td><td></td></tr><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">Seated Lateral Raise</td><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left">3–6 Sets</td><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">6–12 Reps @ 67%–85% Of Your 1RM</td><td>30–90 Seconds</td><td></td></tr><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">Straight Bar Tricep Pushdown</td><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left">3–6 Sets</td><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">6–12 Reps @ 67%–85% Of Your 1RM</td><td>30–90 Seconds</td><td></td></tr><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">Dumbbell Above Head Tricep Extension</td><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left">3–6 Sets</td><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">6–12 Reps @ 67%–85% Of Your 1RM</td><td>30–90 Seconds</td><td></td></tr><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">Cool-Down (Aerobic Exercise)</td><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left"></td><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">5 Minutes</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">Cool-Down (Static Stretches)</td><td class="has-text-align-left" data-align="left"></td><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">30 Seconds Each Exercise</td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
